OL,3,CBeavers set to be legally recognised
OL,4,Cas a native species in Wales
OL,6,FBeavers are set to be legally
OL,7,Frecognised as a native species in
OL,8,FWales, the Welsh Government has
OL,9,Fconfirmed.
OL,11,FIt's hoped the move will help pave the
OL,12,Fway for their managed reintroduction.
OL,14,FClimate change secretary Huw Irranca-
OL,15,FDavies said new legislation would make
OL,16,Fit an offence to deliberately harm
OL,17,Fbeavers or their habitats in Wales.
