OL,3,CBeavers set to be legally recognised
OL,4,Cas a native species in Wales
OL,6,FHe confirmed the law would be changed
OL,7,Fbefore the May 2026 Senedd election,
OL,8,Fbringing Wales in line with Scotland
OL,9,Fand England.
OL,11,FThe announcement came during a debate
OL,12,Fled by Joyce Watson who called for
OL,13,Ftheir reintroduction to act as "eco-
OL,14,Fengineers" in tackling the nature
OL,15,Fcrisis.
OL,17,FMs Watson, the Senedd's beaver
OL,18,Fchampion, made a passionate case for
OL,19,Fbringing the "majestic" animals home `
OL,20,Fcenturies after they were hunted to
OL,21,Fextinction in Tudor times.
