OL,3,CBeavers set to be legally recognised
OL,4,Cas a native species in Wales
OL,6,FShe told Senedd members beavers could
OL,7,Fbe critical to improving water quality
OL,8,Fand reducing flood risk.
OL,10,F'Eco-engineers'
OL,12,FShe said: "Beavers are amazing eco
OL,13,Fengineers, innate wetland managers,
OL,14,Frestoring habitats, increasing
OL,15,Fbiodiversity, preventing flooding, and
OL,16,Fproviding all manner of ecosystem
OL,17,Fservices."
