OL,6,FLeading a short debate on October 1,
OL,7,Fshe raised Wildlife Trusts Wales'
OL,8,Freintroduction project focused on the
OL,9,FDyfi catchment where a small number of
OL,10,Fbeavers are already living wild.
OL,12,FMs Watson said: "In short, re-
OL,13,Festablishing sustainable populations
OL,14,Fcould breathe new life into our water
OL,15,Fsystem for the benefit of both
OL,16,Fwildlife and people."
