OL,6,F'Bring them home'
OL,8,FMs Watson said: "Ultimately, as with
OL,9,Fother once prosecuted animals ` like
OL,10,Fred kites and ospreys ` beavers belong
OL,11,Fto Wales. We removed them; we need to
OL,12,Fbring them home."
OL,14,FHer Labour colleague Carolyn Thomas
OL,15,Fbacked reintroduction, describing
OL,16,Fbeavers as a vital part of the
OL,17,Fecosystem benefiting other species
OL,18,Flike otters, trout and salmon.
