OL,3,CBeavers set to be legally recognised
OL,4,Cas a native species in Wales
OL,6,FShe explained how their dams improve
OL,7,Fwater quality, prevent flooding and
OL,8,Fdrought.
OL,10,FMr Irranca-Davies, who is deputy first
OL,11,Fminister as well as climate secretary,
OL,12,Fsaid he was proud to support the
OL,13,F"transformative" plan for the managed
OL,14,Freintroduction of beavers.
OL,16,FCalling beavers "nature's engineers"
OL,17,Fand a keystone species, he explained
OL,18,Ftheir presence has a
OL,19,Fdisproportionately positive impact on
OL,20,Fbiodiversity and ecosystems.
